John,<br>
     Thanks for the welcome.Count me in on the Spey casting classes provided I can get there from S.W. Okla. I know you will be busy at Conclave this Oct., but if you can work me in, I need some help with my distance casting and any thing else you think I need to work on. I do alot of open water casting to stripers and sandbass from a boat and I could really use the extra distance. Most of the time I'm using Teeny T Series lines on a 5wt. for Sandies and an 8wt. for Stripers. I would be more than happy getting the distance I saw you and Andrew throwing last March.<br>
